      <title>豆腐制造商的股价因在古老工艺中添加自动化而飙升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-17/tofu-maker-s-shares-surge-by-adding-automation-to-ancient-craft</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尽管人们食用更多的植物性蛋白质来源，但许多日本豆腐生产商仍在努力维持经营。山美公司则不然，该公司预计，由于自动化和大规模生产，利润将创历史新高。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-17/tofu-maker-s-shares-surge-by-adding-automation-to-ancient-craft</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 17 Dec 2023 23:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
